{"tid":581341,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"有無咩軟件,可以令到特定的軟件連唔到網絡?","createTime":"2018-03-05T09:16:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T12:09:40.000Z","uid":157021,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b39006dc25d145f7fd63e7519acbde6503dd6ea8","tid":581341,"uid":157021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:16:47.000Z","msg":"有無咩軟件，可以令到特定的軟件連唔到網絡？即係電腦係要可以隨時上網。因為每次都熄個上網功能好煩。想獨立Block左某幾個軟件，方便自己。<br />\n<br />\n即係好似停左 Google Chrome嗰上網功能咁，咁Chorme就上唔到網，但同時間IE就要上到網。<br />\n當然哩個功能我唔係想用係上網Browser。<br />\n<br />\n我想咁多位巴絲，有沒有哩一個概念的軟件可以介紹下？<br />\n<br />\n係Google搵左好耐都搵唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eaf2acca6c2bb8b4cea18adb45dccb52ddccab1","tid":581341,"uid":23094,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:18:25.000Z","msg":"一般防毒軟件都做到"},{"pid":"12127a3f41affe624398434886f23bd39fa03ea1","tid":581341,"uid":70159,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:30:09.000Z","msg":"360"},{"pid":"955868ff08fa6a332192aa10c45e736093cfffb5","tid":581341,"uid":157021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8eaf2acca6c2bb8b4cea18adb45dccb52ddccab1","tid":581341,"uid":23094,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:18:25.000Z","msg":"一般防毒軟件都做到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:51:09.000Z","msg":"明白，試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c05a4663b43f68029f4b8c668cd762297e2f70","tid":581341,"uid":157021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12127a3f41affe624398434886f23bd39fa03ea1","tid":581341,"uid":70159,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:30:09.000Z","msg":"360"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:51:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 盡量唔想用大陸野"},{"pid":"2cb01020566c12f7cca74252ae90e4ece2e047b2","tid":581341,"uid":3647